headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid HSIC and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Henry Schein currently trades at $64.88 per share and has shown little upside over the past six months, posting a middling return of 3.5%. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 34.7% gain during that period.
